Air Tanzania Seeks Investor to Fund Recapitalization, Business Day Reports

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-03-25T04:54:27Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-25/air-tanzania-seeks-investor-to-fund-recapitalization-business-day-reports.html
Tanzania is in talks with investors
interested in buying a stake in the state-owned Air Tanzania
airline, Business Day reported, citing Deputy Transport Minister
Athumani Mfutakamba.  The East African nation plans to recapitalize the airline
under a public-private partnership arrangement, the
Johannesburg-based newspaper said, citing Mfutakamba.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  